er of users and $M$ is the\nnumber of VLC and RF APs. We also show that the best online algorithm to solve\nthis problem can achieve a competitive ratio of $\\log(M)$. Simulation results\nfurther demonstrate the advantages of the hybrid system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 20:57:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Jul 2018 08:43:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-19"}
