d to test this\nsystem have been deposited at a Drosophila stock center, and are available to\nlabs for further, independent testing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 23:55:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2018 22:48:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-02"}
