t do\nnot resolve the CNM should maintain an interstellar thermal pressure within the\ntwo-phase regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jun 2018 14:21:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Jul 2018 19:01:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-25"}
