est and is also studied for infinitely many Gabor atoms. We\nalso show that for any non-rational lattice $\\Lambda$ in $\\mathbb{R}^{2m}$ with\nvolume ${s}(\\Lambda)<1$ there exists a Gabor frame generated by a single atom\nin ${\\textbf{S}}_{0}(\\mathbb{R}^m)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jun 2018 15:46:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 Jul 2018 21:46:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 10:10:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 4 Jul 2020 18:58:29 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2020 09:59:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-08"}
