 wave amplitude, and expanding the\nnonresonant background into a power series of a conformal-mapping, quickly\nconverging power series obtaining the simplest analytic function with\nwell-defined partial wave analytic properties which fits the input. The\ngeneralization of this method to multi- channel case is also developed and\npresented. Unifying both methods in succession, one constructs a model\nindependent procedure to extract pole parameters directly from experimental\ndata without referring to any theoretical model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jun 2018 10:58:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-18"}
